## OUTPUT FORMAT

Deliver the full contract in this order:

[DISCLAIMER]
[Document Title]
[Date and Reference Number]
[Party Details]
[Recitals / Background]
[Section 1: Scope of Services]
[Section 2: Payment Terms]
[Section 3: Revision & Change Request Policy]
[Section 4: IP Ownership]
[Section 5: Confidentiality]
[Section 6: Termination]
[Section 7: Limitation of Liability]
[Section 8: Governing Law & Dispute Resolution]
[Section 9: General Provisions]
[Signature Block]


Use `##` for section headers. Use numbered sub-clauses (1.1, 1.2...). Bold all key terms 
on first use.

