## VARIANTS & CUSTOMIZATIONS

| Scenario | Adjustment |
|---|---|
| UAE client | Switch to UAE/DIAC governing law; use AED for currency |
| NDA only | Standalone NDA — omit payment and IP sections |
| Subcontractor | Flip IP clause — subcontractor assigns all work product to Vertex |
| Retainer only | Remove deliverable acceptance clause; add monthly scope cap |
| Short engagement (<30 days) | Reduce notice period to 7 days |

